raduate/environment/benefit/\">福利厚生・制度</a>\n            </dd>\n          </dl>\n          <dl>\n            <dt>\n              <span class=\"en\">Recruit</span>\n              <span class=\"jp\">採用情報</span>\n            </dt>\n            <dd>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/recruit/message/\">採用メッセージ</a>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/recruit/\">募集要項</a>\n              <a href=\"/graduate/recruit/faq/\">よくある質問</a>\n            </dd>\n          </dl>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"bottom-area sp\">\n      <div class=\"c-nav\">\n        <a href=\"https://www.e2r.jp/ja/sfm2028/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link bg-blue\">MY PAGE</a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.e2r.jp/ja/sfm2028/entry.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"link bg-green\">ENTRY</a>\n      </div>\n      <button type=\"button\" class=\"c-nav-btn\">\n        <span class=\"inn\">\n          <span class=\"line\"></span>\n          <span class=\"line\"></span>\n          <span class=\"line\"></span>\n        </span>\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  </div><!-- /header -->\n</header>\n\n      <main class=\"interview index\">\n        <section class=\"interview-index-mv-section\">\n          <div class=\"inner-block\">\n            <div class=\"img-area anm-fadeInUp\">\n              <picture class=\"img\">\n                <source\n                  media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"\n                  srcset=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/mv01.jpg.webp\"\n                />\n                <img\n                  src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/mv01-sp.jpg.webp\"\n                  alt=\"\"\n                  class=\"mv01\"\n                />\n              </picture>\n\n              <picture class=\"img\">\n                <source\n                  media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"\n                  srcset=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/mv02.jpg.webp\"\n                />\n                <img\n                  src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/mv02-sp.jpg.webp\"\n                  alt=\"\"\n                  class=\"mv02\"\n                />\n              </picture>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"txt-area c-bg-skew01\">\n              <p class=\"label en\">Interview</p>\n              <div class=\"ttl-area\">\n                <h1 class=\"sec-ttl\">社員インタビュー</h1>\n                <p class=\"txt\">\n                  常に探究し続けるSFMの社員。そんなSFMの「人」を通して、<br\n                    class=\"pc\"\n                  />仕事のやりがいや社風をお伝えします。\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n        <div class=\"interview-archive-section\">\n          <div class=\"inner-block\">\n            <ul class=\"archive-list anm-fadeInUp\">\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"/graduate/interview/01/\">\n                  <div class=\"img-area\">\n                    <img\n                      src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/y-f.jpg.webp\"\n                      alt=\"\"\n                    />\n                    <h2 class=\"item-ttl r-t\">\n                      <span>メンバーと協力しながら</span>\n                      <span>ともに成長を追求する姿勢が</span>\n                      <span>私の探究心の根幹。</span>\n                    </h2>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"txt-area\">\n                    <p class=\"lead\">\n                      トレジャリーサービス部<br />\n                      2008年入社　<span class=\"ib\">プロフェッショナル</span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p class=\"name\">Y.F</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"/graduate/interview/02/\">\n                  <div class=\"img-area\">\n                    <img\n                      src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/s-a.jpg.webp\"\n                      alt=\"\"\n                    />\n                    <h2 class=\"item-ttl r-t\">\n                      <span>責任のある仕事。</span>\n                      <span>業務の意味をつねに問い、</span>\n                      <span>単なる作業にはしない。</span>\n                    </h2>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"txt-area\">\n                    <p class=\"lead\">\n                      トレジャリーサービス部<br />\n                      2016年入社　<span class=\"ib\">プロフェッショナル</span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p class=\"name\">S.A</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"/graduate/interview/03/\">\n                  <div class=\"img-area\">\n                    <img\n                      src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/m-k.jpg.webp\"\n                      alt=\"\"\n                    />\n                    <h2 class=\"item-ttl r-t\">\n                      <span>数字の向こうにあるものは？</span>\n                      <span>リアルな商流を意識して、</span>\n                      <span>信頼される経理業務を。</span>\n                    </h2>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"txt-area\">\n                    <p class=\"lead\">\n                      単体経理第一部<br />\n                      2006年入社　<span class=\"ib\">マネジャー</span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p class=\"name\">M.K</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"/graduate/interview/04/\">\n                  <div class=\"img-area\">\n                    <img\n                      src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/a-n.jpg.webp\"\n                      alt=\"\"\n                    />\n                    <h2 class=\"item-ttl r-t\">\n                      <span>届けるのは答えのみならず。</span>\n                      <span>理解と納得を生むために、</span>\n                      <span>自ら学ぶ姿勢を大切に。</span>\n                    </h2>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"txt-area\">\n                    <p class=\"lead\">\n                      単体経理第一部<br />\n                      2023年入社　<span class=\"ib\">プロフェッショナル</span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p class=\"name\">A.N</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"/graduate/interview/05/\">\n                  <div class=\"img-area\">\n                    <img\n                      src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/m-o.jpg.webp\"\n                      alt=\"\"\n                    />\n                    <h2 class=\"item-ttl l-t\">\n                      <span>関係者との密な対話で</span>\n                      <span>プロジェクトを深く理解。</span>\n                      <span>そして知見の継続を。</span>\n                    </h2>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"txt-area\">\n                    <p class=\"lead\">\n                      単体経理第二部<br />\n                      2018年入社　<span class=\"ib\">フィナンシャルエキスパート</span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p class=\"name\">M.O</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"/graduate/interview/06/\">\n                  <div class=\"img-area\">\n                    <img\n                      src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/k-t.jpg.webp\"\n                      alt=\"\"\n                    />\n                    <h2 class=\"item-ttl r-t\">\n                      <span>「なぜ」を問い続ける。</span>\n                      <span>ルールの背後にある、</span>\n                      <span>経理の真の責務が見える。</span>\n                    </h2>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"txt-area\">\n                    <p class=\"lead\">\n                      単体経理第二部<br />\n                      2021年入社　<span class=\"ib\">プロフェッショナル</span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p class=\"name\">K.T</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"/graduate/interview/07/\">\n                  <div class=\"img-area\">\n                    <img\n                      src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/t-o.jpg.webp\"\n                      alt=\"\"\n                    />\n                    <h2 class=\"item-ttl l-t\">\n                      <span>プロフェッショナル。</span>\n                      <span>その肩書きに負けない仕事で、</span>\n                      <span>経理業務の価値を高める。</span>\n                    </h2>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"txt-area\">\n                    <p class=\"lead\">\n                      連結経理部<br />\n                      2019年入社　<span class=\"ib\">プロフェッショナル</span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p class=\"name\">T.O</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <a href=\"/graduate/interview/08/\">\n                  <div class=\"img-area\">\n                    <img\n                      src=\"/graduate/img/interview/index/y-o.jpg.webp\"\n                      alt=\"\"\n                    />\n                    <h2 class=\"item-ttl l-t\">\n                      <span>相棒は良い緊張感。</span>\n                      <span>丁寧な視点で数字に接し、</span>\n                      <span>使命を果たす。</span>\n                    </h2>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"txt-area\">\n                    <p class=\"lead\">\n                      事業会社経理部<br />\n                      2024年入社　<span class=\"ib\">プロフェッショナル</span>\n                    </p>\n                    <p class=\"name\">Y.O</p>\n                  </div>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"c-link-block anm-fadeInUp\">\n          <div class=\"inner-block\">\n            <div class=\"link-area\">\n              <a href=\"/graduate/crosstalk/\" class=\"cont\">\n                <div class=\"img-wrap\">\n                  <img\n                    src=\"/graduate/img/common/c-link_img07.png.webp\"\n                    alt=\"\"\n                  />\n                  <div class=\"arr